00:37.950 --> 00:42.286
♪

00:42.353 --> 00:43.087
Is that the best you've got?

00:43.088 --> 00:44.721
(Crowd chanting)

00:44.722 --> 00:46.489
(Whack)

00:46.490 --> 00:49.258
(Crowd din)

00:49.259 --> 00:50.859
♪

00:55.299 --> 00:56.899
♪

01:01.337 --> 01:02.937
♪

01:07.343 --> 01:10.746
♪

01:11.081 --> 01:13.248
